_cost = total_bails_eaten * hay_cost_per_bail\n\n# Calculate change after buying the hay\nchange = initial_money - total_hay_cost\n\nprint(change)\n```\n```output\n6.0\n```\nThe final answer is \\(\\boxed{6}\\).\n\nWait, let me recheck my solution.\n\n"[0m
